# Local private overrides example.
# Copy this file to a private local file on your server/client and replace placeholders.
# Do not commit real panel paths, tokens, VLESS links, UUIDs, or private keys.

# VPS / management server public IP: keep DIRECT to avoid proxy loops.
IP-CIDR,YOUR_SERVER_IP/32,no-resolve

# Optional: management domains if you later put x-ui/subconverter behind a domain.
# DOMAIN,panel.example.com
# DOMAIN,sub.example.com
